        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Bolstering Innovative Options to Save Immediately on Medicines Act or the BIOSIM Act</b></p> <p>This bill increases Medicare payments for biosimilars for five years. The bill applies to biosimilars for which the average sales price or wholesale acquisition cost is less than that of the reference biological product, as specified.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
